1:1 COMMENT "# listiter.z -- Iterator over a container using a class with .lock field"
1:73 EOL "\n"
2:1 COMMENT "#"
2:2 EOL "\n"
3:1 COMMENT "# Demonstrates:"
3:16 EOL "\n"
4:1 COMMENT "# - Container class with public/private access control"
4:55 EOL "\n"
5:1 COMMENT "# - Class-based iterator with .lock field (Phase 7: classes may hold locks)"
5:76 EOL "\n"
6:1 COMMENT "# - .lock field holding a borrowed reference to the container's privates"
6:73 EOL "\n"
7:1 COMMENT "# - Friend access via .private to read the container's private fields"
7:70 EOL "\n"
8:1 COMMENT "# - Callable iterator (for-loop integration via optionval)"
8:59 EOL "\n"
9:1 COMMENT "# - The container is locked for the lifetime of the iterator"
9:61 EOL "\n"
10:1 EOL "\n"
11:1 COMMENT "# Container with private internals"
11:35 EOL "\n"
